snippet.title: Fossil Corner Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist now! https://store.steampowered.com/app/1587710/

Fossil Corner is a chill fossil collection / puzzle game. You play a retired paleontologist, collecting fossils and solving evolutionary puzzles in your old garage. Coming to PC and Mac Summer '21!

Made by Brady Soglin. Trailer music by Dylan Payne. Voice of Onis McHenry.
